<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000836/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Note
This subject involves mandatory practical activities that must be taken during the school period as they take place in research facilities with specific equipement. If they are not taken during the school period, the maximum grade in the global evaluation cannot be achieved.
Progressive assessment
Mark required to pass the course: > 5/10 (Minimum mark in each part: 4/10). The assessable items are:
Written exam: 50%
Oral presentation: 10%
Deliverables: 30%
Onlines quizzes: 10%
Overall assessment
Mark required to pass the course: > 5/10 (Minimum mark in each part: 4/10). The assessable items are:
Written exam: 70%
Oral presentation: 30%
Extraordinary exam
Mark required to pass the course: > 5/10 (Minimum mark in each part: 4/10). The assessable items are:
Written exam: 80%
Oral presentation: 20%"""@es ;
